{Most good players have an extra restriction in their Weak Two-bid guidelines - they won't 
open with a Weak Two-bid when they hold an outside 4-card Major, even if the hand qualifies 
otherwise. This Deal shows why.

If NORTH opened with 2\S, SOUTH might well pass and a \H game 
would be missed.}

